{"tid":2016494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[畢業論文問卷求幫忙] 反修例運動國際線嘅問卷","createTime":"2020-05-14T11:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T12:49:02.000Z","uid":355266,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f2bc1b8c5ecee9423e6a457bb1627582ae23870","tid":2016494,"uid":355266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T11:57:41.000Z","msg":"各位手足，唔知可唔可以幫手做份有關反修例運動國際線嘅問卷， master畢業論文用的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到去問卷右上角可以揀語言<br />\n<a href=\"http://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_8vHUlSrOfWgRast\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcuhk.au1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_8vHUlSrOfWgRast&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7iK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=42e6fe32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cuhk.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_8vHUlSrOfWgRast</a><br />\n<br />\n份paper主要係從社會心理學角度出發，想搵吓有啲乜嘢因素驅使人去參與國際線嘅行動，而「國際線」究竟會唔會對參加者/非參加者有啲咩影響/轉變。得出嚟個result係諗住思考吓「國際線」可以點走落去，如果份嘢寫得正正常常，第時有機會可能share個結果出嚟大家一齊討論吓。<br />\n<br />\n為咗保障各位，份問卷係匿名的，亦set好唔會記錄IP等等任何可以識別到受訪者的個人資料。份問卷全部都係選擇題，除咗問你大概參加過幾多次唔同類型嘅活動之外，唔會問到你參加嘅任何細節，希望可以令大家放心啲。當然，保護自己好緊要，做到一半想唔做，可以隨時退出。<br />\n<br />\n所以如果做完份問卷覺得可以的話，大家都可以推吓同埋share俾身邊親朋好友去做。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位可以幫幫手，感謝! 如有任何意見，都歡迎留底個comment! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n送上J圖一張:<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/73252838_143052873729749_5436431069106667520_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=2d5d41&amp;_nc_ohc=6WPBHWKfRDEAX9iR2Rz&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=4fafe93b886c8d60a498fa620fd42f0a&amp;oe=5EC74D08\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F73252838_143052873729749_5436431069106667520_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3D2d5d41%26_nc_ohc%3D6WPBHWKfRDEAX9iR2Rz%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3D4fafe93b886c8d60a498fa620fd42f0a%26oe%3D5EC74D08&h=9603792c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69236045_1250300895094290_8992316132203429888_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=eYRXi_6Cg2AAX9qgfN1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=ec1887588d762c0f3de1c1ba5dd018b5&amp;oe=5EE43CAB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69236045_1250300895094290_8992316132203429888_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DeYRXi_6Cg2AAX9qgfN1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26oh%3Dec1887588d762c0f3de1c1ba5dd018b5%26oe%3D5EE43CAB&h=9c5e8745&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de2e634ad06c7fe76aebbed6c07c9c0a1a74aa9d","tid":2016494,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:00:37.000Z","msg":"pretty well - designed <br />\n<br />\ndone and add oil !!!!"},{"pid":"cfa246f80df4eef0fd7351bf2bdb2752fddb993c","tid":2016494,"uid":355266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de2e634ad06c7fe76aebbed6c07c9c0a1a74aa9d","tid":2016494,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:00:37.000Z","msg":"pretty well - designed <br />\n<br />\ndone and add oil !!!!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:05:18.000Z","msg":"多謝晒!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果覺得可以都可以分享俾身邊不同人做，都想個sample可以廣泛啲多啲人參與，希望個結果會有代表性啲"},{"pid":"706d2c3b2c7f0e1afc6079f9d92c36a9ba2afe9d","tid":2016494,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfa246f80df4eef0fd7351bf2bdb2752fddb993c","tid":2016494,"uid":355266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de2e634ad06c7fe76aebbed6c07c9c0a1a74aa9d","tid":2016494,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:00:37.000Z","msg":"pretty well - designed <br />\n<br />\ndone and add oil !!!!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:05:18.000Z","msg":"多謝晒!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" c